{"text_id":108161,"tokens":["How"," to"," Study"," and"," Understand"," the"," Diseases"," Which"," Are"," Associated"," With"," the"," Hormone"," Cor","tisol","\n\n","Learn"," about"," the"," importance"," of"," the"," hormone"," cortisol",".","\n\n","Cor","tisol"," secretion"," by"," the"," adrenal"," cortex"," is"," under"," a"," negative"," feedback"," control"," in"," which"," its"," excess"," in"," the"," blood"," inhibits"," the"," secretion"," of"," the"," pituitary"," hormone"," adren","ocor","tico","t","ropic"," hormone",".","\n\n","Know"," about"," the"," functions"," of"," cortisol",".","\n\n","People"," who"," administer"," cortisol"," as"," an"," anti","-","inflammatory"," agent"," can"," develop"," diabetes"," if"," the"," administration"," of"," the"," hormone"," is"," for"," a"," long"," time"," such"," as"," occurs"," with"," people"," under"," a"," constant"," requirement"," to"," take"," this"," hormone"," as"," a"," supplement"," due"," to"," its"," deficiency"," in"," the"," body",".","\n\n","Learn"," about"," the"," main"," disorders"," that"," involve"," cortisol",".","\n\n","The"," second"," cause"," of"," c","ushing"," syndrome"," is"," excessive"," secretion"," of"," the"," adren","ocor","tico","t","ropic"," hormone"," (","AC","TH",")"," by"," the"," pituitary"," gland"," itself"," or"," due"," to"," ec","topic"," secretion"," of"," this"," hormone"," by"," a"," malignant"," tumor"," in"," the"," body",".","\n\n","The"," other"," cause"," is"," ec","topic"," secretion"," of"," this"," hormone"," which"," can"," be"," caused"," for"," example"," due"," to"," a"," malignant"," tumor"," of"," the"," lungs",".","\n\n","In"," addition"," to"," these"," two"," causes"," which"," involve"," secretion"," of"," the"," ACT","H"," in"," excessive"," amount"," to"," the"," blood"," circulation"," by"," the"," pituitary"," gland"," and"," which"," is"," called"," c","ushing"," disease",","," the"," adrenal"," cortex"," itself"," can"," undergo"," pathological"," condition"," in"," which"," a"," tumor"," of"," the"," adrenal"," cortex"," can"," over","se","crete"," cortisol"," causing"," symptoms"," of"," c","ushing"," syndrome",".","\n\n","The"," adrenal"," cortex"," can"," have"," adeno","ma"," or"," carcinoma"," which"," are"," possible"," causes"," of"," over","se","cretion"," of"," the"," hormone"," cortisol",".","\n\n","The"," other"," disorder"," which"," involves"," cortisol"," is"," add","ison","'","s"," disease"," or"," hypo","cor","tisol","ism",".","\n\n","Addison","'","s"," disease"," is"," manifested"," by"," increased"," secretion"," of"," ACT","H"," which"," is"," over","secre","ted"," due"," to"," the"," lack"," of"," the"," negative"," feedback"," that"," cortisol"," usually"," makes"," on"," the"," secretion"," of"," ACT","H",".","\n\n","This"," is"," caused"," due"," to"," the"," secretion"," of"," melan","ocytes"," stimulating"," factors"," by"," the"," pituitary"," gland"," the"," thing"," that"," increases"," the"," pigmentation"," of"," the"," skin",".","\n\n","Step"," ","1",":"," Learn"," about"," the"," Normal"," Physiology"," of"," Cor","tisol","\n","----------------","--------","\n\n","*","   ","Cor","tisol"," is"," a"," steroid"," hormone"," produced"," by"," the"," adrenal"," cortex",","," which"," is"," the"," outer"," layer"," of"," the"," adrenal"," gland",".","\n","*","   ","The"," adrenal"," gland"," is"," a"," small"," gland"," located"," on"," top"," of"," the"," kidney",".","\n","*","   ","Cor","tisol"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," various"," physiological"," processes",","," including"," glucose"," metabolism",","," immune"," function",","," and"," stress"," response",".","\n\n","Step"," ","2",":"," Understand"," the"," Role"," of"," Cor","tisol"," in"," Stress"," Response","\n","----------------","----------------","----------------","--","\n\n","*","   ","Cor","tisol"," is"," often"," referred"," to"," as"," the"," \"","stress"," hormone","\""," because"," it"," is"," released"," in"," response"," to"," stress",".","\n","*","   ","Cor","tisol"," helps"," the"," body"," to"," respond"," to"," stress"," by"," increasing"," blood"," sugar"," levels",","," suppressing"," the"," immune"," system",","," and"," aiding"," in"," the"," metabolism"," of"," fat",","," protein",","," and"," carbohydrates",".","\n","*","   ","Cor","tisol"," also"," helps"," the"," body"," to"," recover"," from"," stress"," by"," regulating"," the"," body","'","s"," response"," to"," stress"," and"," promoting"," the"," return"," to"," homeostasis",".","\n\n","Step"," ","3",":"," Learn"," about"," the"," Disorders"," Associated"," with"," Cor","tisol"," I","mbal","ance","\n","----------------","----------------","----------------","----------------","\n\n","*","   ","C","ushing","'","s"," syndrome",":"," a"," disorder"," caused"," by"," excessive"," secretion"," of"," cortisol",","," leading"," to"," symptoms"," such"," as"," weight"," gain",","," high"," blood"," pressure",","," and"," changes"," in"," appearance",".","\n","*","   ","Addison","'","s"," disease",":"," a"," disorder"," caused"," by"," insufficient"," secretion"," of"," cortisol",","," leading"," to"," symptoms"," such"," as"," fatigue",","," weight"," loss",","," and"," changes"," in"," skin"," pigmentation",".","\n","*","   ","Ad","renal"," insufficiency",":"," a"," disorder"," caused"," by"," insufficient"," secretion"," of"," cortisol",","," leading"," to"," symptoms"," such"," as"," fatigue",","," weight"," loss",","," and"," changes"," in"," skin"," pigmentation",".","\n\n","Step"," ","4",":"," Understand"," the"," Causes"," of"," Cor","tisol"," I","mbal","ance","\n","----------------","----------------","----------------","-","\n\n","*","   ","P","ituitary"," tumors",":"," tumors"," that"," can"," cause"," excessive"," secretion"," of"," ACT","H",","," leading"," to"," Cushing","'","s"," syndrome",".","\n","*","   ","Ad","renal"," tumors",":"," tumors"," that"," can"," cause"," excessive"," secretion"," of"," cortisol",","," leading"," to"," Cushing","'","s"," syndrome",".","\n","*","   ","Ec","topic"," ACT","H"," production",":"," production"," of"," ACT","H"," by"," tumors"," outside"," the"," pituitary"," gland",","," leading"," to"," Cushing","'","s"," syndrome",".","\n","*","   ","Genetic"," disorders",":"," disorders"," such"," as"," congenital"," adrenal"," hyperplasia",","," which"," can"," cause"," cortisol"," imbalance",".","\n","*","   ","Inf","ections",":"," infections"," such"," as"," tuberculosis",","," which"," can"," cause"," adrenal"," insufficiency",".","\n\n","Step"," ","5",":"," Recognize"," the"," Symptoms"," of"," Cor","tisol"," I","mbal","ance","\n","----------------","----------------","----------------","-","\n\n","*","   ","Weight"," gain"," or"," loss","\n","*","   ","Changes"," in"," appetite","\n","*","   ","Fatigue","\n","*","   ","Changes"," in"," skin"," pigmentation","\n","*","   ","High"," blood"," pressure","\n","*","   ","Changes"," in"," mood","\n","*","   ","Changes"," in"," menstrual"," cycle","\n\n","Step"," ","6",":"," Diagnose"," Cor","tisol"," I","mbal","ance","\n","----------------","----------------","---","\n\n","*","   ","Blood"," tests",":"," to"," measure"," cortisol"," levels"," in"," the"," blood",".","\n","*","   ","Urine"," tests",":"," to"," measure"," cortisol"," levels"," in"," the"," urine",".","\n","*","   ","Imaging"," tests",":"," such"," as"," CT"," or"," MRI"," scans",","," to"," identify"," tumors"," in"," the"," pituitary"," gland"," or"," adrenal"," glands",".","\n","*","   ","Insulin"," tolerance"," test",":"," to"," measure"," cortisol"," response"," to"," insulin",".","\n\n","Step"," ","7",":"," Treat"," Cor","tisol"," I","mbal","ance","\n","----------------","----------------","-","\n\n","*","   ","Medication",":"," to"," reduce"," cortisol"," levels"," in"," Cushing","'","s"," syndrome"," or"," to"," replace"," cortisol"," in"," Addison","'","s"," disease",".","\n","*","   ",